sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant CI as case_ingestion.py
    participant BL as blob_storage.py
    participant AZB as Azure Blob
    participant EM as embeddings.py
    participant AZE as Azure OpenAI
    participant VS as AzureSearch VectorStore
    participant AZS as Azure AI Search

    Admin->>UI: close case action
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/case
    Note over SR: intent=CASE_INGESTION
    Note over SR: action=CLOSE_CASE
    Note over SR: handle_case_entry() L96
    Note over SR: validate action L100-104
    SR->>SR: _dispatch_entry_handler() L82
    SR->>EH: handle_entry(envelope) L84
    Note over EH: intent == CASE_INGESTION L65
    EH->>EH: _handle_case_ingestion() L66
    Note over EH: action = CLOSE_CASE L74

    EH->>CI: CaseEntryService.get_case(case_id) L107
    CI->>BL: CaseRepository.load(case_id) L102
    Note over BL: download_json("{case_id}.json") L20
    BL->>AZB: get_blob_client().download_blob()
    AZB-->>BL: raw JSON bytes
    BL-->>CI: case_doc dict

    CI->>CI: IncidentFactory.from_blob_doc()
    Note over CI: d_states (not phases)
    Note over CI: D1_2 (not D1_D2)
    Note over CI: status (not header.completed)
    Note over CI: opened_at (not opening_date)

    CI->>CI: build document_text
    CI->>CI: _build_doc_id() L509

    CI->>EM: generate_embedding(document_text) L52
    Note over EM: get_embeddings() lru_cache L19
    Note over EM: text-embedding-3-large
    EM->>AZE: embeddings.create()
    AZE-->>EM: vector list[float] dim=3072
    EM-->>CI: embedding vector

    CI->>CI: build metadata dict
    CI->>VS: _get_case_vector_store() L30
    Note over VS: AzureSearch(case_index_v3)

    CI->>AZS: add_texts([content_text], metadatas, ids)
    AZS-->>CI: [doc_id]

    CI->>BL: CaseRepository.save(case_id) L107
    Note over BL: upload_json("{case_id}.json") L17
    BL->>AZB: upload_blob(data, overwrite=True)
    AZB-->>BL: ok
    BL-->>CI: saved

    CI-->>EH: indexed=True
    EH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=accepted
    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope
    UI-->>Admin: success
